[06/09/2023]
- Appearance:
- + New Female Hairs (Freya's favorite hair style).
- Drugs:
- + Completely new Weed system
- + Same: Corner Selling.
- + Differences:
> New way of buying weed (buying seeds instead of bricks).
> Making Bags of weed by drag and drop 10g stack onto Empty Silicone Bag.
> Making Weed Brick by right clicking on Dried Bud (Dried Weed) (option to calculate the brick weight if you got Scale on you).
> Growing Weed, 30 minutes of completion to be able to harvest the Weed Tree (Must Water & Fertilize as before).
> Make your own Strain while fertilizing, continue using the same to increase the quality. Better Quality? Better Benefits.. Find your own.
> Watering Can is empty, you have to fill it by dragging over it a Weed Water.
> Harvesting the tree you're getting a Wet Weed Tree, need 3Hour of calm to get dried weed.
> Make a brick, find the dealer and start a sell run.

